- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is also likely as the paper discusses big data processing, which is related to distributed computing. 
- cs.DB (Databases) is another likely category as the paper discusses big data analysis, which is related to databases. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is less likely but still possible as the paper may touch upon security issues related to the proposed network paradigm. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also less likely but possible as the paper may discuss the use of AI in big data analysis.
